

**Purchase invoice**

The details of the CONAI contributions can be specified on the documents, from CONAI purchase / sale setup:

<img width="" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000216-0/33CONAI(1).png"><br>

**Sales invoice**

Also Sales side (on page CONAI Purchase/Sale SETUP) you can choose whether to expose the details of the contributions or just the caption related to CONAI paid, or both:

<img width="750" src="https://docs.eos-solutions.it/Images/PR000216-0/34CONAI(1).png"><br>

